OL,3,CHit-and-run driver jailed after
OL,4,Ckilling man in his 70s in fatal car
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FA man's been jailed after killing a
OL,8,Fman in his 70s in a car which the
OL,9,Fdriver had stolen earlier that day in
OL,10,FBirmingham.
OL,12,FTyrone Clarke, 50, of Gisborne
OL,13,FGardens, hit the man with a grey
OL,14,FToyota on Highters Heath Lane, shortly
OL,15,Fafter 7:30pm on Tuesday 4 November
OL,16,F2025.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
