PN,34902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782193687
OL,3,CHit-and-run driver jailed after
OL,4,Ckilling man in his 70s in fatal car
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FHe was seriously hurt and died at the
OL,8,Fscene. The driver of the Toyota, which
OL,9,Fhad been stolen earlier that day was
OL,10,Ffound by police officers around half a
OL,11,Fmile away, badly damaged.
OL,13,FAccording to the police's
OL,14,Finvestigation, Clarke walked away from
OL,15,Fthe damaged vehicle before calling a
OL,16,Ftaxi to take him home to Evesham.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
