OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782193687
OL,3,CHit-and-run driver jailed after
OL,4,Ckilling man in his 70s in fatal car
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FAt Birmingham Crown Court, Clarke was
OL,8,Fjailed for six years and nine months
OL,9,Fand disqualified from driving for more
OL,10,Fthan 10 years. He will also have to
OL,11,Ftake an extended test before ever
OL,12,Fbeing allowed to drive again.
OL,14,FDet Sgt Julie Lyman, from SCIU, said:
OL,15,F"Our investigators found that Clarke's
OL,16,Fdangerous driving, in a stolen car,
OL,17,Fcaused a man's death.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
