OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782193687
OL,3,CHit-and-run driver jailed after
OL,4,Ckilling man in his 70s in fatal car
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,F"Our thoughts throughout our
OL,8,Finvestigation have remained with the
OL,9,Fman's family, and they have been
OL,10,Fsupported and updated by our
OL,11,Fspecialist officers.
OL,13,F"Clarke callously left the scene and
OL,14,Fcalmly called a taxi to collect him,
OL,15,Fclearly thinking he would be able to
OL,16,Fget away with what he'd done.
OL,18,F"I hope his conviction and sentence
OL,19,Fsends a clear message to drivers to
OL,20,Fthink about the effect their actions
OL,21,Fcan have."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUzD@AOU}D@JO]
